{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 54,
  "title": "第五十四章（善觀）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "善建者不拔 善抱者不脫 子孫以祭祀不絕"
    },
    {
      "text": "修之身 亓德乃真 修之家 亓德有餘 修之鄉 亓德乃長 修之邦 亓德乃豐 修之天下 亓德乃博"
    },
    {
      "text": "以身觀身 以家觀家 以鄉觀鄉 以邦觀邦 以天下觀天下"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾何以知天下然茲 以此"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善以道抱精神者，終不可拔引解脫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為人子孫能修道如是，長生不死，世世以久，祭祀先祖，宗廟無絕時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於身，愛氣養神，益壽延年。其德如是，乃為真人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於家，父慈子孝，兄友弟順，夫信妻貞。其德如是，乃有餘慶及於來世子孫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於鄉，尊敬長老，愛養幼少，教誨愚鄙。其德如是，乃無不覆及也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "修道於國，則君信臣忠，仁義自生，禮樂自興，政平無私。其德如是，乃為豐厚也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人主修道於天下，不言而化，不教而治，下之應上，信如影響。其德如是，乃為普傳。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之身，觀不修道之身，孰亡孰存也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之家，觀不修道之家。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之鄉，觀不修道之鄉也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之國，觀不修道之國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以修道之主，觀不修道之主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言，吾何知天下修道者昌，背道者亡。以此五事觀而知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不貪於多，齊其所能，故不脫也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "子孫傳此道以祭祀則不輟也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以身及人也，修之身則真，修之家則有餘，修之不廢，所施轉大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 45
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼皆然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以天下百姓心觀天下之道也，天下之道，逆順吉凶，亦皆如人之道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此上之所云也。言吾何以得知天下乎，察己以知之，不求於外也，所謂不出戶以知天下者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
